Protesters came out on an overpass over the 101 Freeway in Los Angeles to protest against deportations of illegal aliens in California. Citizen journalist Austen Fletcher asked them about their reasons for protesting. Warning: Graphic language Some of the highlights? John the protester with the Anonymous mask is disturbed with President Donald Trump’s ‘feminihst’ regime. […]
